# Private agent config. No trailing slash: `dotagents link` makes .agents a
# symlink, which git treats as a file, so a directory-only `.agents/` would not
# match it. The sanitized design log is NOT in here — it lives in design/ at the
# repo root and is tracked, because CHANGELOG.md cites its D-numbers (D56).
.agents
*.local.md
CLAUDE.local.md
.claude/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
src/*.egg-info/

# dotagents CLI package build artifacts (release artifacts, not committed)
dist/
*.pyz
.venv/
.venv-test/

# OS/editor
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
